- qlut - specify look up table
- new qimage variant (new command?) to use LUTs
- qxaxis

e.g.: qxaxis(y0, [x0 x1], '1 min')
      qxaxis(y0, [x0:dx:x1])
      qxaxis(y0, [x0 x1], [xa:dx:xb], 'Time (s)')
      qxaxis(y0, [x0 x1], [xa xb xc], {'A', 'B', 'C'}, 'Time (s)')

- qmticks: add minor ticks to current axis
- qticklen: prespecifies tick length (could be zero); -ve is left/up
- qlabeldist: where do tick labels go; -ve is left/up; specified from end
  of ticks. Two numbers: separate distance for axis title.

- qarrow

- documentation!
